text: Inge Sedlmaier (4 May 1925 - 13 March 1976) was a German gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:1976 deaths Category:German female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Landshut
